---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="bg-black py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">Aortic Root Deformation Analysis</h1>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-gray-300 space-y-8">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Our advanced deformation analysis provides a computational framework for quantifying and visualizing structural changes in the aortic root following Transcatheter Aortic Valve Replacement (TAVR) procedures, enabling precise postoperative assessment.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white pt-6 border-t border-gray-700">Key Analytical Objectives</h2>
          
          <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Precise Structural Measurement</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 pl-5">
              <li>Tracking of deformations across all anatomical sections</li>
              <li>Detailed structural analysis with quantitative metrics</li>
              <li>Sectional deformation rate measurement (3 or 6 sections per slice)</li>
              <li>Voxel-based analysis calculating deformation ratios between models</li>
            </ul>
          </div>        
          
          <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-md p-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Centerline Coordinate Analysis</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 pl-5">
              <li>Centerline curve points stored in JSON format with (x, y, z) coordinates</li>
              <li>Integration with Image Viewer to generate cross-sections using centerline coordinates</li>
              <li>Precise spatial mapping of aortic root geometry</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. Volumetric Regions of Interest</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 pl-5">
              <li><strong>Left Ventricular Outflow Tract (TSVI)</strong></li>
              <li><strong>TAVI to Annulus (TAVR)</strong></li>
              <li><strong>Annulus to Coronary Artery (RING)</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">4. Statistical Analysis</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 pl-5">
              <li><strong>Basic statistics:</strong> Mean, median, standard deviation, coefficient of variation</li>
              <li><strong>Range analysis:</strong> Minimum, maximum, data range</li>
              <li><strong>Distribution percentiles:</strong> 25th, 50th (median), 75th percentiles</li>
              <li><strong>Normality assessment:</strong> Below, within, and above normal range classification</li>
              <li><strong>Trend analysis:</strong> Maximum slope, max slope slice, total data points</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg mt-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Clinical Applications</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Our deformation analysis provides critical insights for clinical decision-making:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 pl-5">
            <li>Enables personalized treatment planning and valve selection</li>
            <li>Predicts long-term structural responses to TAVR implantation</li>
            <li>Provides patient-specific anatomical adaptation metrics</li>
            <li>Supports postoperative monitoring and intervention planning</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="mt-12 mb-8 flex justify-start max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <a href="/HistaviWeb/registration" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-neutral-800 hover:bg-neutral-700 rounded-lg text-white transition-colors duration-200">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.707 14.707a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414l4-4a1 1 0 011.414 1.414L5.414 9H17a1 1 0 110 2H5.414l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 010 1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
      </svg>
      Previous: Registration
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>